# Forex Backtester

## 🚀 Overview
A modular Python backtester for OANDA FX pairs, with an interactive Streamlit dashboard.

## 📂 Repo Layout
- `backtester.py` – core engine & CLI
- `indicators.py` – RSI, ATR, MA, signal-strength
- `simulator.py` – ATR-based trailing stops
- `strategy.py` – entry logic, returns `Trade` objects
- `trade.py` – `Trade` class + `to_dict()`
- `dashboard.py` – Streamlit UI
- `main.py` – alternative CLI entry point

